channel.desc: Drama, Family 2022 A sharp-tempered civil servant sets out on a solo journey, abandoning everything after receiving tragic news about his health. Influenced by his situation, he aims to leave a lasting impact before he leaves this world. Bill Nighy, Alex Sharp, Adrian Rawlins, Hubert Burton, Oliver Chris, Aimee Lou Wood, Oliver Hermanus, Kazuo Ishiguro.
